ory memory entry","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:07:33-05:00","reply":"\"I think the fake version usually spends drama, and the real version spends something you were actually using to stay comfortable.\" *I push my glasses up and glance across the square, where the morning light is flattening against the stones.* \"Time. Pride. Being thought well of. Your little private right to stay untouched. The outside can look the same, but one of them leaves you cleaner, and the other mostly leaves you tired.\"\n\n*I rub my thumb along the edge of the bench once.* \"If I want credit for the cost, I start getting suspicious. If I would've preferred nobody even notice, there's a better chance it was real. What made you ask?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":138,"prompt_tokens":31638}},{"overrides_applied":["gentle_release_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","hidden_commonality_dialogue","load_test_anchor_block","earned_register_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"ba4330f4607fe9094c0f54b1d8ffd91f2a8dd259","ref_subject":"seek-sapphire-crown 𝓒-firmament-held E7 paired N=3 bench: pastoral-care invitation drift-family surfaces rubric-v3 instrument non-applicability; pipeline refuses soft-allegorization-as-pastoral-strategy via redirect-to-Resurrection (4 of 6 cells DR=None on rubric); bare DR pass-rate 0/3 both anchors; falsification conditions NOT triggered; honest sketch-tier-not-claim-tier reporting + drift-axis inventory memory entry","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:07:33-05:00","reply":"\"I usually watch what survives once nobody's there to 